{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":160,"arguments_yes_count":0,"arguments_no_count":0,"id":423,"created_at":"2015-10-05T15:10:27+0200","updated_at":"2015-10-05T15:10:27+0200","body":"<p>L&rsquo;article 20 de la loi n&deg; 78-753 du 17 juillet 1978 portant diverses mesures d&#39;am&eacute;lioration des relations entre l&#39;administration et le public et diverses dispositions d&#39;ordre administratif, social et fiscal (loi CADA) est modifi&eacute; comme suit :<\/p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Au troisi&egrave;me alin&eacute;a, apr&egrave;s le mot &ldquo;avis&rdquo; est ajout&eacute; &ldquo;conforme&rdquo;. La phrase suivante est ins&eacute;r&eacute;e : &ldquo;La commission peut assortir ses d&eacute;cisions d&rsquo;astreinte ou de sanctions.&rdquo;<\/p>","versions_count":2,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":0,"author":{"username":"Conseil National du Num\u00e9rique","displayName":"Conseil National du Num\u00e9rique","uniqueId":"conseilnationaldunumerique","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/409_default_avatar.png"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/conseilnationaldunumerique","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":86,"title":"Section 1","subtitle":"Ouverture des donn\u00e9es publiques","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[],"modals":[],"votes":[{"user":{"username":"Benoit Phuez","displayName":"Benoit Phuez","uniqueId":"benoitphuez","isAdmin":false,"media":{"url":"\/media\/cache\/default_avatar\/default\/0001\/01\/191_default_avatar.jpg"},"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/benoitphuez","settings":"https